
=Bio=

"Jim is currently a Lead Software Systems Engineer in department E542, '''Open Services, at The MITRE Corporation'''. E542 is part of the Information Technologies directorate of MITRE’s Center for Air Force C2 Systems working out of the Bedford, Massachusetts location. At age 30, James has more than ten years experience in software development as a consultant or contractor and seven years experience with the open source community."


